@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix schema: <http://schema.org/> .

@prefix iq: <urn:iq:>.
@prefix ai: <urn:ai:>.

## IQ is your operating environment for neuro-symbolic cognitive AI.

### Learner Onboarding
ai:LearnerOnboardingWorkflow a schema:Action ;
                              schema:name "Learner Onboarding" ;
                              schema:description "Workflow for onboarding new learners to JIN's platform" ;
                              iq:initial ai:HelloLearner .

### Step 1: Welcome Message for Learner
ai:HelloLearner a schema:Action ;
                 schema:name "Welcome Message" ;
                 schema:description "JIN sends a welcome message to the new learner" ;
                 iq:to ai:LearnerProfileSetup .

### Step 2: Learner Profile
ai:LearnerProfileSetup a schema:Action ;
                        schema:name "Learner Profile" ;
                        schema:description "Assist the learner in setting up their profile" ;
                        iq:to ai:Started .

### Other steps specific to learner onboarding can be defined here...

