# Define the onboarding workflows for Fantasy and Tokenomics roles

### Fantasy Onboarding
ai:FantasyOnboardingWorkflow a schema:Action ;
                              schema:name "Fantasy Onboarding" ;
                              schema:description "Embark on a journey into immersive fantasy worlds and discover endless adventures tailored to your preferences." ;
                              iq:initial ai:HelloFantasy .

### Step 1: Welcome Message for Fantasy
ai:HelloFantasy a schema:Action ;
                 schema:name "Welcome Message" ;
                 schema:description "Welcome to the realm of fantasy! Start your journey and unlock the magic within." ;
                 iq:to ai:FantasyProfileSetup .

### Step 2: Fantasy Profile
ai:FantasyProfileSetup a schema:Action ;
                        schema:name "Fantasy Profile" ;
                        schema:description "Customize your character and preferences to begin your epic adventure in the world of fantasy." ;
                        iq:to ai:PreferencesConfiguration .

### Other steps specific to fantasy onboarding can be defined here...

### Tokenomics Onboarding
ai:TokenomicsOnboardingWorkflow a schema:Action ;
                                 schema:name "Tokenomics Onboarding" ;
                                 schema:description "Navigate the world of cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology with confidence and expertise." ;
                                 iq:initial ai:HelloTokenomics .

### Step 1: Welcome Message for Tokenomics
ai:HelloTokenomics a schema:Action ;
                    schema:name "Welcome Message" ;
                    schema:description "Research blockchain assets, cryptocurrencies and AI tokens." ;
                    iq:to ai:TokenomicsProfileSetup .

### Step 2: Tokenomics Profile
ai:TokenomicsProfileSetup a schema:Action ;
                           schema:name "Tokenomics Profile" ;
                           schema:description "Get started by setting up your preferences and gaining insights into the fascinating world of tokenomics." ;
                           iq:to ai:PreferencesConfiguration .

### Other steps specific to tokenomics onboarding can be defined here...

